Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,============TEXT ============
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.52,0:00:17.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直 一直都想见你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.37,0:00:29.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样好吗 如此激动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.06,0:00:33.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的眼神好像在问我为什么要出现呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.63,0:00:38.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天你好像过的很愉快嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.78,0:00:43.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才会出现在你面前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.94,0:00:48.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当愉快这种感情将你内心动摇的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.98,0:00:52.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最不想见的人就会出现
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.28,0:00:54.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是讽刺呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.51,0:00:59.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就这么不想见我吗 优库里伍德
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.77,0:02:37.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定是我的上司把和路塞伊斯大人掳走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.05,0:02:39.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.62,0:02:43.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我接到了杀死和路塞伊斯大人的指令
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.36,0:02:47.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 为什么塞拉会接到杀死优的指令
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.13,0:02:51.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞拉的目的不是把优带回忍者村吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.64,0:02:55.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会变成杀死优啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.81,0:03:03.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\a6}你恨我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.96,0:03:05.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那当然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.61,0:03:08.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亏我当时还那么相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.01,0:03:13.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还以为两个人可以就那样一直在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.12,0:03:14.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\a6}办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.86,0:03:16.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.39,0:03:20.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你无法原谅杀死7th abyss的我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.42,0:03:22.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你才对我说了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.78,0:03:27.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「消失吧」这样冷酷的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.40,0:03:33.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是很遗憾 当时我确实消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.94,0:03:38.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但并非是从世上消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.24,0:03:39.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\a6\fad(16,166)}你的愿望是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.25,0:03:46.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愿望吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.45,0:03:50.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这个来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.41,0:03:54.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在这种地方很让我吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.97,0:03:57.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过更让我吃惊的是你竟然还交上了朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.26,0:04:01.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呀 要说我的愿望的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.78,0:04:06.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之所以会下暗杀指令
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.75,0:04:08.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为我的组织认为
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.11,0:04:13.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅加洛来袭是和路塞伊斯大人的魔力所导致的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.19,0:04:16.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞拉菲姆 这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.38,0:04:19.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真无聊 这种指令肯定无效的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.21,0:04:23.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要说的这么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.29,0:04:24.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 你要杀死优吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.34,0:04:28.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这问题你不问就不知道答案吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.11,0:04:30.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那答案不是很清楚了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.10,0:04:32.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.84,0:04:34.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那又怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.40,0:04:39.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 我自己去找和路塞伊斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.36,0:04:44.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你等一下 你们这些吸血忍者怎么都这么死脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.38,0:04:46.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想做的事情不做就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.47,0:04:52.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你根本就不懂「任务」的分量有多重
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.89,0:04:57.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能违反规定 所以我才要成为你的新娘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.85,0:05:00.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优的生命没有任务重要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.37,0:05:02.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这种说法太卑鄙了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.24,0:05:03.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于我们吸血忍者来说…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.47,0:05:05.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些话我已经听腻了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.15,0:05:08.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的要杀死优吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.88,0:05:11.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以叫你不要问些明摆着的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.04,0:05:14.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没问你这个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.24,0:05:16.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你究竟是想杀她还是不想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.94,0:05:20.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有问吸血忍者 而是在问塞拉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.49,0:05:24.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能会想杀死她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.58,0:05:27.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞拉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.26,0:05:32.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经够了吧 步和耍叶子的都别吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.77,0:05:36.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在去找死灵师不是更重要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.42,0:05:40.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.53,0:05:45.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.35,0:05:54.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你总是很坦率呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.63,0:05:57.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用奉承我 真恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.55,0:05:59.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.78,0:06:00.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.28,0:06:03.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也全靠你我想明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.34,0:06:05.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个任务我放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.05,0:06:08.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.34,0:06:11.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一定要找到优啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.75,0:06:16.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 等等 不要连目标都没有就乱跑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.87,0:06:20.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 看的正起劲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.79,0:06:22.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想拜托你 优库里伍德
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.10,0:06:27.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也只有你能实现我的愿望了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.17,0:06:30.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也要来看看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.22,0:06:36.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家好像都在拼命找你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.51,0:06:38.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来看看嘛 来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.22,0:06:55.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是你还继续把我的话当耳旁风…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:05.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.45,0:07:15.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,步
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.09,0:07:17.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相川
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.66,0:07:21.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个东西怎么会突然就倒下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.97,0:07:23.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.50,0:07:24.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,步 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.93,0:07:25.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.93,0:07:28.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 但脸好像被压坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.22,0:07:31.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 原来原本就是长这样子的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.97,0:07:38.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在只是稍微让你见识一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.81,0:07:40.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后可能就会发生更可怕的事情了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:46.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看 你又动摇了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.11,0:08:00.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.97,0:08:01.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅加洛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.15,0:08:04.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 没有穿校服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.21,0:08:10.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死灵师的人偶？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.19,0:08:16.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙 快闪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.24,0:08:22.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春奈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.32,0:08:28.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为啥我会得宠？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.32,0:08:29.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个河童是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.28,0:08:31.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道吗 你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.71,0:08:34.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黄瓜除了生吃还可以煮着吃炒着吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.88,0:08:36.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.59,0:08:38.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧 我现在就把你拉出来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.43,0:08:41.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 让我来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.05,0:08:43.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点蛆虫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.78,0:08:44.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撑住
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.68,0:08:49.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油 还差一点 加油 春奈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.68,0:08:49.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\a6}邪恶的我看到这里以为是在生孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.13,0:08:53.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\a6}别伤害春奈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.11,0:08:53.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不是我干的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.90,0:08:57.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把它召唤过来的不是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.21,0:09:01.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是再明白不过了吗 优库里伍德
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.67,0:09:04.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的心一动摇就会招来灾祸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.07,0:09:11.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不正是因为这样你才发誓不说话不动摇的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:14.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.57,0:09:18.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唤来死亡之人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.92,0:09:33.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 打扰你们说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.87,0:09:36.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.67,0:09:40.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得你是玛蒂莱依斯魔法学校的老师吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.18,0:09:44.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认识我呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.57,0:09:50.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 你的传闻已经传到冥界了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.18,0:09:54.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌 究竟是怎么样的传闻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.98,0:09:57.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说你很强
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.23,0:10:00.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.84,0:10:04.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺便问下 你找我有什么事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.33,0:10:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看见我的学生被整成那样 我可不能坐视不理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.81,0:10:23.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\a6}死灵战士大战怪物人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.89,0:10:26.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\a6}春奈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.63,0:10:30.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘剑·燕返
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.20,0:10:35.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.90,0:10:39.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就…300%
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.17,0:10:43.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,400 500 600
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.11,0:10:46.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.53,0:10:49.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.63,0:10:51.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春奈 坚持住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.63,0:10:53.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.23,0:10:55.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你想干什么 友纪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.74,0:10:58.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弄倒 弄倒后拉开它
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.79,0:11:00.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春奈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.90,0:11:02.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋 滚开 你这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.90,0:11:06.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相川 塞拉菲姆 把它推开 快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.82,0:11:08.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 这家伙太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.31,0:11:10.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.72,0:11:12.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 动呀 动呀 动呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.17,0:11:15.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动啊啊啊啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.13,0:11:18.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.47,0:11:26.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是玛蒂莱依斯魔法学校的大师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.10,0:11:30.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过奖了 没什么了不起的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.82,0:11:33.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧 友纪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.97,0:11:35.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.88,0:11:37.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么东西 刚才那束光
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.72,0:11:41.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撑住 梅尔·修德罗姆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.17,0:11:42.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吸我的血
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.83,0:11:46.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认母体异常 术式限制解除
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.53,0:11:54.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才这下是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.96,0:11:57.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汝乃生命之分歧点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.29,0:12:02.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一咏唱确认 术式解放
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.90,0:12:04.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,友纪 你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.82,0:12:10.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾走向生路 汝去往死路
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.91,0:12:12.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二咏唱确认
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.81,0:12:14.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咬碎吧 Masticore
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.97,0:12:18.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最终咏唱确认
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.61,0:12:21.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是刚才那家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.18,0:12:24.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃下那招可就连灰都不剩了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.76,0:12:28.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 看来没带着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.21,0:12:33.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「没办法 就帮帮你们吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.21,0:12:33.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\a6}和魔装少女咒语一样 玩倒句
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.05,0:12:38.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mystletainn
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.07,0:12:39.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.13,0:12:41.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别废话了 快变身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.16,0:12:47.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘剑·燕返
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.31,0:12:49.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.53,0:12:50.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3Q 塞拉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.77,0:12:58.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「虽然我可爱又迷人 但我会招来死亡」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.66,0:13:01.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,融化冻结的心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.52,0:13:05.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一咏唱确认 解放术式
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.18,0:13:13.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汝将会把众神的气息化作暴风雪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.65,0:13:16.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二咏唱确认
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.55,0:13:20.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奔跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.56,0:13:23.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,absolute Fenrir
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.94,0:13:26.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最终咏唱确认
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.91,0:13:41.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暴走了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.10,0:13:46.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此 这就是京子所说的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.36,0:13:48.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的最强魔装兵器吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.14,0:13:51.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.84,0:13:56.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她可以算是我旧友的妹妹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.54,0:13:59.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来还想让相川收留她一阵子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.85,0:14:05.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\a6}会停下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.46,0:14:04.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有解除装置喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.10,0:14:09.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是设定成自动关闭的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.39,0:14:13.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦暴走 也有自爆的可能性呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.71,0:14:16.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 如果出现了这种情况的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.03,0:14:18.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出现了这种情况的话？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.54,0:14:23.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能期望相川来解决问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.08,0:14:27.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春奈时也是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.07,0:14:31.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他可是个了不起的魔法使啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.61,0:14:35.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底发生什么了 为什么那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.66,0:14:37.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她到底是何方神圣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.53,0:14:39.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她身后那个玩意很怪异吧 很可怕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.25,0:14:41.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.69,0:14:42.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞拉 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.39,0:14:46.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,步 为什么要阻止我 这么下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.77,0:14:48.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能出手 对手可是友纪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.25,0:14:53.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是今天和我们疯玩了一整天的伙伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.63,0:14:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不明白 忍者无论何时都该不惧危险上前战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.43,0:15:00.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是规定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.00,0:15:03.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就知道你会那么说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.97,0:15:06.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这里能交给我来处理吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.37,0:15:09.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解了 可是如果你失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.99,0:15:12.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就用剑把你插成刺猬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.45,0:15:13.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.31,0:15:19.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没辙了 步 你可要想办法摆平啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.66,0:15:26.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,友纪 你在干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.57,0:15:29.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认不出我们了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.11,0:15:41.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.05,0:15:45.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的 我是僵尸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.44,0:15:48.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你到底是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.23,0:15:52.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.18,0:15:57.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你会在哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.30,0:16:00.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相川…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.78,0:16:02.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.32,0:16:05.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就来救你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.33,0:16:08.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认母体异常
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.40,0:16:11.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距离自爆装置启动之前 还剩30秒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.25,0:16:15.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.53,0:16:17.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚才说了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.27,0:16:19.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相川
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.38,0:16:22.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.82,0:16:26.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 这到底是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.71,0:16:29.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别进来 别进入我的内心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.43,0:16:34.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等着 等着我 友纪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.38,0:16:45.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相川
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.45,0:16:48.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是离开这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.02,0:16:52.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别过来 不然…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.41,0:16:56.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然连你都会被一起炸飞的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.34,0:17:04.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\a6}10…9…8…7…6
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.46,0:17:02.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.37,0:17:04.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让这种事发生啊啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.22,0:17:13.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走开 叫你走开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.42,0:17:18.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的会爆炸喔 没必要连你也一起陪葬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.12,0:17:19.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快离开 快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.76,0:17:23.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没用的 快离开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.65,0:17:27.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不离开 我绝对不离开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.63,0:17:28.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,友纪（yuki）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.93,0:17:50.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捡回一条命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.20,0:17:52.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相川
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.78,0:17:57.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来 友纪（tomonori）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.51,0:18:01.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫你妹的tomonori啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.00,0:18:05.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧 和我说的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.90,0:18:08.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是步
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.45,0:18:09.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.02,0:18:13.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人不可貌相 他相当有一手嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.25,0:18:22.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优库里伍德 在你实现我的愿望之前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.80,0:18:24.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不会放弃的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.11,0:18:34.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 我的话还没说完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.41,0:18:45.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\a6}我戳 我戳 我戳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.38,0:18:44.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全煮熟了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.81,0:18:46.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一股焦味儿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.58,0:18:49.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和路塞伊斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.14,0:18:53.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去哪了啊 我们到处找你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.61,0:18:56.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么关系嘛 来 我们回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.28,0:19:07.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我走这边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.11,0:19:08.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.36,0:19:12.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那再见了 路上小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.62,0:19:15.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相川
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.31,0:19:20.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今 今天谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.82,0:19:22.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.54,0:19:26.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.21,0:19:39.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\a6}你们先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.72,0:19:39.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子饿了吗 我也陪你一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.57,0:19:44.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 别回来的太晚了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.07,0:19:51.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身上都是灰 我先回去烧洗澡水了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.92,0:20:03.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.58,0:20:12.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶尔大家一起玩玩也不坏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.37,0:20:23.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永别了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.99,0:20:29.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都怪我 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.93,0:20:33.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果没有我 今天就不会发生这种事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.13,0:20:39.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,步和春奈还有塞拉 都对我施以温柔的话语
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.98,0:20:44.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这让我很高兴 而我也毫不顾忌的接受了这份好意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.67,0:20:50.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我是无法和他人在一起的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.17,0:20:53.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.19,0:21:00.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直以来让你们受了不少苦 很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.99,0:21:04.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我继续待在你们身边 总有一天…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.21,0:21:06.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定又会害的某人伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.86,0:21:08.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.33,0:21:10.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唤来死亡之人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.34,0:21:15.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 永别了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.04,0:21:26.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下雪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.12,0:21:30.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要大到让这地区的人都能看到的大雪喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.39,0:21:33.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望厨艺可以双倍增强
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.23,0:21:38.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望我的料理可以让这里的人们笑容常在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.69,0:21:42.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果可以的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.66,0:21:47.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我和步他们…永远在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.45,0:22:05.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\a6}希望她们的愿望都不要实现  步
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.30,0:22:09.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.45,0:22:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么只有我的愿望实现了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.43,0:22:17.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我会写下这种混账愿望啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.22,0:22:22.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.46,0:22:24.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.23,0:22:27.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优库…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.79,0:22:32.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还在烦恼个什么劲啊 僵尸步
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.43,0:22:36.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 步 又不是生离死别
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.08,0:22:40.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切才刚开始呢 黏黏的纳豆 步
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.38,0:22:47.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说这种明摆着的事了 春奈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.51,0:22:52.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 不是黏黏的纳豆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.86,0:22:54.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是Never give up（永不放弃）
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.94,0:24:39.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\a6}出去狩猎 不过恐怕反而会被吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.63,0:24:27.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道什么叫political correctness
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.88,0:24:28.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听起来就像paris collection一样
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.86,0:24:31.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说词语表达起来不带男女差别的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.53,0:24:33.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是像空姐之类的词？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.90,0:24:36.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我和塞拉菲姆不称自己是女忍
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.37,0:24:37.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.25,0:24:39.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也成为吸血忍者吧
